text: Knema muscosa is a species of plant in the family Myristicaceae. It is a tree endemic to Borneo where it is confined to Sarawak. ==References== muscosa Category:Endemic flora of Borneo Category:Trees of Borneo Category:Flora of Sarawak Category:Vulnerable plants Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot Category:Taxa named by James Sinclair (botanist)
